videos.description: Romello White has his eyes on the prize after being left alone, but George King hustles in and swats away the layup.
videos.headline: Colorado's King says 'no, no, no' to White

videos.description: Kodi Justice hits the wide open corner-three to give the Sun Devils an 11-0 lead out of the gate.
videos.headline: Justice caps off 11-0 start for ASU

videos.description: Tra Holder lurks on defense, comes up with the sneaky steal and then hits the transition three to boost the Sun Devils lead before half.
videos.headline: Holder steals and scores

videos.description: Remy Martin goes on a personal run of 3 buckets in just over a minute, finishing off the run with a long 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Martin drains three from way downtown

videos.description: McKinley Wright IV shows off his ball-handling skills and drives all the way to the basket for the layup and the foul.
videos.headline: Wright gets tough bucket to drop plus the foul

videos.description: Tyler Bey goes up strong and finishes with the off-balance layup to take the lead then Namon Wright throws down the exclamation point.
videos.headline: Buffs take lead and then follow it with emphatic dunk

videos.description: Tra Holder and the ASU offense move quickly in transition and Holder finishes with the up-and-under layup and the foul.
videos.headline: Holder nails impressive layup to get within 1

videos.description: Mickey Mitchell stays persistent underneath by grabbing the strong offensive board and goes for the high priority shot to send the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Mitchell jams to send game to overtime

videos.description: McKinley Wright IV comes down with the offensive board and goes back up strong to give the Buffs a lead in overtime.
videos.headline: Colorado's Wright scoops in layup to take the lead in OT
